library EmergencyMedicineEmergencyDepartmentUtilizationofCTforMinorBluntHeadTraumaforPatientsAged2Through17Years version '1.0.000'

using QDM version '5.4'

include MATGlobalCommonFunctions version '3.0.000' called Global

codesystem "CPT": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.12' 
codesystem "LOINC": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.1' 
codesystem "SNOMEDCT": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.96' 

valueset "Brain Tumor": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1011' 
valueset "Coagulopathies": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1002' 
valueset "Dangerous Mechanism of Injury": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1018' 
valueset "Emergency Department Visit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1520' 
valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837' 
valueset "Head CT": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1008' 
valueset "Headache": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1027' 
valueset "Loss of Consciousness": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1012' 
valueset "Non Penetrating Head Trauma": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1007' 
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1' 
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591' 
valueset "Physical Signs of Basilar Skull Fracture": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1017' 
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836' 
valueset "Signs of Altered Mental Status": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1016' 
valueset "Ventricular Shunt": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1010' 
valueset "Ventricular Shunt Device": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1035' 
valueset "Vomiting": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.17.4077.3.1015' 

code "Critical care, evaluation and management of the critically ill or critically injured patient; first 30-74 minutes": '99291' from "CPT" display 'Critical care, evaluation and management of the critically ill or critically injured patient; first 30-74 minutes'
code "Glasgow coma scale": '35088-4' from "LOINC" display 'Glasgow coma scale'
code "Severe (severity modifier) (qualifier value)": '24484000' from "SNOMEDCT" display 'Severe (severity modifier) (qualifier value)'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
  ["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
  ["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
  ["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
  ["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period":
  ( ( ["Encounter, Performed": "Emergency Department Visit"]
  	union ["Encounter, Performed": "Critical care, evaluation and management of the critically ill or critically injured patient; first 30-74 minutes"] ) EDVisit
  	where exists ( EDVisit.diagnoses EncounterDiagnosis
  			where EncounterDiagnosis in "Non Penetrating Head Trauma"
  	) ) EDVisitMP
  	where EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"

define "Head CT Ordered During ED Visit for Minor Blunt Head Trauma":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	with ["Diagnostic Study, Order": "Head CT"] HeadCTOrdered
  		such that HeadCTOrdered.authorDatetime during EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod

define "Initial Population":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	with ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] BirthDate
  		such that Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod)>= 2
  			and Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod)< 18

define "Denominator":
  "Initial Population"
  	intersect "Head CT Ordered During ED Visit for Minor Blunt Head Trauma"

define "Patient Has Brain Tumor":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	with ["Diagnosis": "Brain Tumor"] BrainTumor
  		such that BrainTumor.prevalencePeriod overlaps EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod

define "Patient Has Coagulopathy":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	with ["Diagnosis": "Coagulopathies"] Coagulopathy
  		such that Coagulopathy.prevalencePeriod overlaps EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod

define "Denominator Exclusions":
  "Patient Has Brain Tumor"
  	union "Patient Has Coagulopathy"
  	union "Patient Has Ventricular Shunt"

define "Patient Has Ventricular Shunt":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	with ( ["Diagnosis": "Ventricular Shunt"]
  		union ["Device, Applied": "Ventricular Shunt Device"] ) VentricularShunt
  		such that VentricularShunt.prevalencePeriod overlaps before EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod
  			or VentricularShunt.relevantPeriod overlaps before EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod

define "Patient Does Not Show Signs of Altered Mental Status After Minor Blunt Head Trauma":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	without ( ["Symptom": "Signs of Altered Mental Status"] ) AlteredMentalStatus
  		such that AlteredMentalStatus.prevalencePeriod overlaps EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod

define "Patient Does Not Show Signs of Basilar Skull Fracture After Minor Blunt Head Trauma":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	without ( ["Symptom": "Physical Signs of Basilar Skull Fracture"] ) FractureSigns
  		such that FractureSigns.prevalencePeriod overlaps EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod

define "Patient Does Not Show Symptom of Severe Headache After Minor Blunt Head Trauma":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	without ( ["Symptom": "Headache"] ) Headache
  		such that Headache.prevalencePeriod overlaps EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod
  			and Headache.severity ~ "Severe (severity modifier) (qualifier value)"

define "Patient Does Not Show Symptom of Vomiting After Minor Blunt Head Trauma":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	without ( ["Symptom": "Vomiting"] ) Vomiting
  		such that Vomiting.prevalencePeriod overlaps EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod

define "Patient Does Not Have Loss of Consciousness After Minor Blunt Head Trauma":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	without ( ["Symptom": "Loss of Consciousness"] ) LOC
  		such that LOC.prevalencePeriod overlaps EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod

define "Emergency Department Visit With Minor Blunt Head Trauma Not Due to Dangerous Mechanism of Injury":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	where not exists ( EDVisitMP.diagnoses EncounterDiagnosis
  			where EncounterDiagnosis in "Dangerous Mechanism of Injury"
  	)

define "No Glasgow Coma Scale Score Less Than 15 During Emergency Department Visit":
  "Emergency Department Visit with Minor Blunt Head Trauma During Measurement Period" EDVisitMP
  	without ["Assessment, Performed": "Glasgow coma scale"] GCS
  		such that GCS.authorDatetime during EDVisitMP.relevantPeriod
  			and GCS.result < 15

define "Numerator":
  "No Glasgow Coma Scale Score Less Than 15 During Emergency Department Visit"
  	intersect "Patient Does Not Have Loss of Consciousness After Minor Blunt Head Trauma"
  	intersect "Patient Does Not Show Signs of Basilar Skull Fracture After Minor Blunt Head Trauma"
  	intersect "Patient Does Not Show Symptom of Severe Headache After Minor Blunt Head Trauma"
  	intersect "Patient Does Not Show Signs of Altered Mental Status After Minor Blunt Head Trauma"
  	intersect "Patient Does Not Show Symptom of Vomiting After Minor Blunt Head Trauma"
  	intersect "Emergency Department Visit With Minor Blunt Head Trauma Not Due to Dangerous Mechanism of Injury"
